{"tid":1532971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「極！緊！急！」831黑警真係打死人！！？","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:08:58.000Z","uid":217605,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"ec374af362f5887783dccae8edce2a344aaa07ba","tid":1532971,"uid":217605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GqnVz5L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGqnVz5L.png&h=c1a2abe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（真係）我朋友個老婆講㗎！！我朋友已報上蘋果！<br />\n<br />\n佢同事嘅老公係警察（C.I.P)，嚟緊呢一兩年就退休。佢今朝被總部call返去同班鬼頭開會&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n原來當晚吐白泡嗰個示威者，喺當場其實已經犧牲咗&hellip;&hellip;嗰兩小時關站，就係經荔枝角站送咗去明愛醫院！同埋暫時所知係，打死人嗰個唔係&ldquo;香港警察&rdquo;！<br />\n<br />\n依家仲想畀掩口費佢阿媽！如果佢接受，聽日就會火化條屍。聽聞位烈士嘅阿媽都係新香港人&hellip;&hellip; 暫時未知佢決定係點&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nMTR車站嘅錄影Recond都唔會keep好耐，所以佢哋越遲公佈越好！！ <br />\n<br />\n但係就算佢被滅聲，我哋．香港人都要發大佢！唔可以畀佢好似大陸咁做嘢呀！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉自Facebook"},{"pid":"1968dde02a0810b2fbab860d1c24aaac55fef58d","tid":1532971,"uid":293648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3227818/org/4660e8b4bf488245b9f9509af60cd498.jpg/j9JFSTPsaqpJe3YzzeG8dFhZzri8CMoMi9IHzaHSB80?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3227818%2Forg%2F4660e8b4bf488245b9f9509af60cd498.jpg%2Fj9JFSTPsaqpJe3YzzeG8dFhZzri8CMoMi9IHzaHSB80%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=266d07ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190831/s00001/12d08c78da352be461abbc1d0922ff2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190831%2Fs00001%2F12d08c78da352be461abbc1d0922ff2d.jpg&h=c098c2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/fbff83/f/800x0/https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69597698_10158010418262448_3537375600886939648_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101